{"id": 2135, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么时候咔嚓一下，你觉得青春期就结束了？", "description": "伤感。", "record_count": 3301, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180123110353X19So3ylHjhdUETs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-24T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 261635, "content": "难过的事情变多了，也再也不用揪着别人说出来，自己消化消化就没事了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245958}, {"id": 262660, "content": "一群好友出去吃饭要订两桌，一桌给孩子老婆们。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250086}, {"id": 261636, "content": "给女儿喂奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245792}, {"id": 261637, "content": "突然发现身边流行的歌曲后知后觉，自己不再能够张口就来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204658}, {"id": 264454, "content": "慢慢接受有些人离开的事实时", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258849}, {"id": 261639, "content": "最喜欢的欧洲杯，最爱的球星的场次，选择睡觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227209}, {"id": 261895, "content": "开始要考四级的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911009}, {"id": 263432, "content": "不再默默喜欢一个男生的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20180203145739se5Vt7CbdrU14mEL", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253539}, {"id": 267016, "content": "生活压力大于学业压力的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122868}, {"id": 261385, "content": "没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没没结束...的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218760}, {"id": 261641, "content": "到了干坏事要坐牢的年纪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187483}, {"id": 261642, "content": "90后再无18岁的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115941}, {"id": 261643, "content": "大概是…脱发的时候吧………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245184}, {"id": 261899, "content": "碰上99的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246638}, {"id": 261388, "content": "不长痘吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781970}, {"id": 261644, "content": "熬夜肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943264}, {"id": 261645, "content": "青春期的时候觉得自己的青春完蛋了 青春期期后觉得自己的青春还没开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243385}, {"id": 266254, "content": "马上要到来的18岁生日", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268121}, {"id": 262159, "content": "工作了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247605}, {"id": 261647, "content": "认识到自己要掌握自己的生活，不在意别人看法时", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238479}, {"id": 261648, "content": "是时候学会长大的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226443}, {"id": 261649, "content": "我想把这个话题分享给某个人，又选择取消的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245991}, {"id": 262930, "content": "看到这个问题竟然有回答冲动的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248825}, {"id": 261650, "content": "当我照镜子看见抬头纹影响了我的颜值时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245990}, {"id": 262419, "content": "当电脑好几天没有开过的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462618}, {"id": 261651, "content": "回忆起大学生活，觉得既熟悉又遥远，像是回忆一个梦的时候。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218756}, {"id": 263444, "content": "英语听力念到衬衫的价格是九磅十五便士的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990903}, {"id": 261652, "content": "熬不了夜，逛不了街，秋天开始睡觉灌暖袋，冬天再也不能嘚瑟穿裙子…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291921}, {"id": 261908, "content": "十年前不再是98年是2008了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823106}, {"id": 261653, "content": "发现自己需要努力挣钱了，父母基本不会给你钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245995}, {"id": 261909, "content": "开始化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636072}, {"id": 261654, "content": "去五道口没有boy来撩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702030}, {"id": 261910, "content": "发现再也不用努力背书考试了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246672}, {"id": 261911, "content": "发现熬夜之后疲惫不堪时，发现再远的风景其实在心里时，发现原来自己走过的路不一样时候.....回头时刻会眼泪打转时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245740}, {"id": 262424, "content": "我才18 我就已经觉得青春回不去了..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249385}, {"id": 261656, "content": "发现家庭经济状况不佳", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236169}, {"id": 261912, "content": "当小孩子开始叫自己阿姨的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 261401, "content": "当我开始试着合群的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245596}, {"id": 261657, "content": "不管怎么浪，就是不长痘痘了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769510}, {"id": 261402, "content": "结婚，势在必行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245598}, {"id": 261658, "content": "开始有皱纹了ರ_ರ 心塞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181800}, {"id": 264475, "content": "当看到之前的追的星或者剧，动漫的时候，恍惚一下就这样十年过去了啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103565}, {"id": 261659, "content": "穿百褶裙，中筒袜加白鞋，也不见得自己能年轻多少，反而觉得装嫩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871396}, {"id": 262172, "content": "生完孩子后，以前很多的事 ，记头不记尾或记尾不记头。熬不起夜，折腾不起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664608}, {"id": 261404, "content": "不敢约炮，OVER", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228271}, {"id": 261660, "content": "感觉自己再也不会轻易爱上一个女孩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245097}, {"id": 261405, "content": "发现时间过得很快的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153320}, {"id": 261661, "content": "不再喜怒无常的适时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212565}, {"id": 262174, "content": "我想，是梅西退役的那一天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904473}, {"id": 262430, "content": "半夜想起日渐衰老的父母会哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249424}]}